snippet.title: Arcade Game: Quantum (1982 Atari) [Re-Uploaded]
snippet.description:
An vector-based outline/maze game similar to "Disco No. 1" and "Qix".

This is the first commercial video game to use a 16-bit microprocessor 68000 CPU for more detailed sound and graphics.

Note: Previously Uploaded. Re-Uploaded for better quality.
